s teaming up withSesame Streetto bringElmoand his friends to Paris as part of its comprehensive coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024 this summer.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.4084724404970813e-12, \"text\": \"STAMFORD\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\", \"score\": 0.9999999993478923, \"rank\": 6.457391780742331e-10, \"text\": \"NEW\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\"}, {\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\", \"score\": 0.9999977591476277, \"rank\": 2.169250993904941e-06, \"text\": \"YORK\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.310256816738968e-13, \"text\": \"N.Y.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.470781198981869e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement was made this morning whenCookie Monsterappeared onTODAY.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elmo, Cookie Monster,Abby Cadabby, andTangowill be featured in activations acrossSesame Street'ssocial media platforms leading into and during the Games, including the U.S. Olympic Team Trials and the Opening Ceremonies of the Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Cadabby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abby Cadabby\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Cadabby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Cadabby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pre-Games activations will feature belovedSesame Streetmuppets in bespoke illustrations detailing their hot air balloon journey fromSesame Streetacross the Atlantic Ocean to Paris.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.470781198981869e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following their arrival in Paris, NBCU will incorporate the Sesame team into its comprehensive social and broadcast coverage surrounding the Games.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.470781198981869e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Elmo, Cookie Monster and the Muppets ofSesame Streetare some of the most beloved characters in American culture,\\\" saidLyndsay Signor, SVP, Consumer Engagement, NBC Sports.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999805998685694, \"rank\": 1.9400496121243036e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.4466935231965552, \"rank\": 0.7421717759653759, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics and Sesame Street both have broad appeal and reach across all ages and backgrounds, and we can not wait to see Elmo and his friends in Paris this Summer in support of our Olympic coverage.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6542599952095603e-26, \"text\": \"Elmo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\"}, {\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.470781198981869e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"P.S., Cookie Monster - we will be sure to have some macarons waiting for you!\\\"\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sesame Street, the Olympics, and NBC are all cultural touchstones and we are excited to join NBC Sports' exemplary coverage of the Olympics,\\\" saidSamantha Maltin, EVP, Chief Marketing and Brand Officer, Sesame Workshop.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999574086676123, \"rank\": 4.258739086905616e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1927, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.4466935231965552, \"rank\": 0.7421717759653759, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics celebrates the best in sportsmanship and promotes kindness and respect, traits that are central to our mission to help children grow smarter, stronger, and kinder to build a better world.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bringing Elmo, Cookie Monster, Abby, and Tango to Paris will provide fun, entertaining, and enriching content for viewers of all generations.\\\"\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cookie Monster\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\"}, {\"begin\": 2287, \"end\": 2291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999999644333009, \"rank\": 3.394934702526223e-08, \"text\": \"Abby\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Newman\"}, {\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tango\", \"score\": 0.9711601143528685, \"rank\": 0.027988427127303758, \"text\": \"Tango\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tango\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tango\"}, {\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.470781198981869e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Elmo is very excited to go to Paris to cheer on all the athletes at the Olympics,\\\" said Elmo.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.470781198981869e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2489, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6542599952095603e-26, \"text\": \"Elmo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And Elmo is also excited to do a little sightseeing.Elmo can not wait to get an eyeful of the Tower.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2500, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6542599952095603e-26, \"text\": \"Elmo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elmo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get it?\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eyeful Tower!Hee hee hee.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris, here we come!\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gooooo teams!\\\"\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Me love sports almost as much as me love cookies!\\\"\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"added Cookie Monster.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cookie Monster\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cookie_Monster\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Me so excited about all da events, but especially da discus throw.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dat one really look delicious.\\\"\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just can not wait to get to Paree!\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(That's how you pronounce it, Elmo.)\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be MAGICAL!\\\"\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"said Abby.\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9999999644333009, \"rank\": 3.394934702526223e-08, \"text\": \"Abby\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abby_Newman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT NBCUNIVERSAL  NBCUniversal is one of the world's leading media and entertainment companies in the development, production, and marketing of entertainment, news, sports and information to a global audience.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.99999804837816, \"rank\": 1.9516258378634646e-06, \"text\": \"NBCUNIVERSAL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.99999804837816, \"rank\": 1.9516258378634646e-06, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal owns and operates a valuable portfolio of news and entertainment television networks, a premier motion picture company, significant television production operations, a leading television stations group, world-renowned theme parks, and a premium ad-supported streaming service.\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3169, \"end\": 3181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.99999804837816, \"rank\": 1.9516258378634646e-06, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3459, \"end\": 3471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.99999804837816, \"rank\": 1.9516258378634646e-06, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 3491, \"end\": 3510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Comcast Corporation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT SESAME WORKSHOP  Sesame Workshop is the global impact nonprofit behindSesame Streetand so much more.\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3519, \"end\": 3534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sesame_Workshop\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SESAME WORKSHOP\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sesame_Workshop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sesame_Workshop\"}, {\"begin\": 3536, \"end\": 3551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sesame_Workshop\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sesame Workshop\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sesame_Workshop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sesame_Workshop\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For over 50 years, we have worked at the intersection of education, media, and research, creating joyful experiences that enrich minds and expand hearts, all in service of empowering each generation to build a better world.\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our beloved characters, iconic shows, outreach in communities, and more bring playful early learning to families in more than 150 countries and advance our mission to help children everywhere grow smarter, stronger, and kinder.\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 4071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learn more atwww.sesameworkshop.organd follow Sesame Workshop onInstagram,X,Facebook, andTikTok.\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"--PARIS 2024--  A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4186, \"end\": 4196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999991878212, \"rank\": 8.120877261755782e-10, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623